{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, you know, when-- I mean, of course I didn't necessarily see it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we passed [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Goeth ?] You know-- you heard of [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Goeth? ?] The lageralteste, you know, the [? lager-- ?] [? theater. ?] You know, who used to just shoot people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, we knew about it, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I've seen him on his balcony many times, you know, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was lucky by-- You did see him in the balcony?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw him [INAUDIBLE] on the Appellplatz, you know, and different, you know, and different places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So actually, we were kind of afraid, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't have no choice, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to go by, and head down, you know, so he doesn't see us, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we shouldn't be obvious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, of course, there was the, the regular Appellplatz, you know, where we used to all come out in the morning and stand in lines, you know, from each barrack, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then different things was going on at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there was this [NON-ENGLISH] and his wife, who were the lageraltestes, you know, from the-- in other words, they were Jewish, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were the Jewish overseers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there was hangings and punishments and all kind of different things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then later on, you know, they were building some office buildings, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they used to-- sort of like from grass or something, they were pressed, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they used to use that for wall or partitions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we had to plaster it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
